&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For over 25 years, Global Relay has set the standard in enterprise information archiving with industry-leading cloud archiving, surveillance, eDiscovery, and analytics solutions. We securely capture and preserve the communications data of the world’s most highly regulated firms, giving them greater visibility and control over their information and ensuring compliance with stringent regulations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Though we offer competitive compensation and benefits and all the other perks one would expect from an established company, we are not your typical technology company. Global Relay is a career-building company. A place for big ideas. New challenges. Groundbreaking innovation. It’s a place where you can genuinely make an impact – and be recognized for it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We believe great businesses thrive on diversity, inclusion, and the contributions of all employees. To that end, we recruit candidates from different backgrounds and foster a work environment that encourages employees to collaborate and learn from each other, completely free of barriers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(224, 62, 45);&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Start your career with us at Global Relay!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we’re looking for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re seeking ambitious young professionals eager to kickstart their careers. Whether you’re new to the world of Co-op or already have a couple terms under your belt, we have exciting opportunities for you in:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Software Development: &lt;/strong&gt;Participate in the creation and improvement of products that define industry standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Science:&lt;/strong&gt; Use of data, analytics and machine learning to guide stakeholders to make the best decision possible.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DevOps:&lt;/strong&gt; Streamlining the software lifecycle so teams can respond faster to customer needs and market changes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Other co-op opportunities may be available as well, please keep an eye on our job boards for all openings.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we value:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A drive to learn and step out of your comfort zone to explore the various areas that may interest you and are passionate about.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for tackling complex challenges with creativity, and resourcefulness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to quality, integrity, candor, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A collaborative spirit and ability to thrive in dynamic, cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;A focus on professional development with mentorship and growth opportunities.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Competitive salary&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;State of the art office facilities and amenities including a top chef team providing delicious breakfast and lunch daily.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;An inclusive and supportive culture that celebrates diverse perspectives.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you can expect:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Global Relay, there’s no ceiling to what you can achieve. It’s the land of opportunity for the energetic, the intelligent, the driven. You’ll receive the mentoring, coaching, and support you need to reach your career goals. You’ll be part of a culture that breeds creativity and rewards perseverance and hard work. And you’ll be working alongside smart, talented individuals from diverse backgrounds, with complementary knowledge and skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Global Relay is an equal-opportunity employer committed to diversity, equity, and inclusion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We seek to ensure reasonable adjustments, accommodations, and personal time are tailored to meet the unique needs of every individual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To learn more about our business, culture, and community involvement, visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.globalrelay.com&quot;&gt;www.globalrelay.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
